Titolo: Final Fantasy Brave Exvius

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Final Fantasy Brave Exvius is a free-to-play role-playing game developed by Alim and published by Square Enix for iOS, Android and Amazon Fire devices. A spin-off of the Final Fantasy series, the game marks as the first collaborative effort between Square-Enix and Alim. As of August 2019, the app had been downloaded over 40 million times worldwide. A tactical RPG spin-off titled War of the Visions: Final Fantasy Brave Exvius was announced to be released in Japan on November 14, 2019, and globally on March 25, 2020.

Genere: Role-playing game

Valutazione: 73
